<p>The Trek Marlin 5 mountain bike is very versatile. This bike comes with a Shimano drivetrain and is an amazing value. Some have complained that they needed to replace the tires and drivetrain after purchasing this bike. However, I believe the components included in the entry-level bike are capable of performing well.</p>



