<p>The Pan di Stelle are roughly the size of Oreos, but they have a similar thickness to chocolate chip cookies. Sugar stars are iced on top of the cookies, and some sugar sprinkles are dotted around the stars. While I was admiring the cookies on my plate, the cocoa’s aroma invited me to take a bite!</p>



<h2>Taste Test</h2>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img data-attachment-id="16065" data-permalink="http://thejourneyndestination.com/2022/05/15/italian-chocolate-and-iced-sugar-star-cookies-pan-di-stelle/20220511_111755/" data-orig-file="https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_111755.jpg" data-orig-size="4032,1816" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{

}" data-image-title="20220511_111759" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_111759.jpg?w=300" data-large-file="https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_111759.jpg?w=1024" src="https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_111759.jpg?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-16067" srcset="https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_111759.jpg?w=1024 1024w, https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_111759.jpg?w=2048 2048w, https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_111759.jpg?w=150 150w, https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_111759.jpg?w=300 300w, https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_111759.jpg?w=768 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>In my first bite, the cookie’s holistic flavor note was a combination of chocolate breakfast cereal and cookies – the breakfast vision is identifiable. To my taste buds, the cookie had a slight reminiscence to one of my favorite <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://thejourneyndestination.com/2020/05/07/ultimate-milk-chocolate-and-white-chocolate-breakfast-cereal/" target="_blank">chocolate breakfast cereals</a>. The fabulous taste and quality of the cocoa, which is <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.barillagroup.com/en/brands/pan-di-stelle/" target="_blank">sourced</a> from a chocolate producer called Barry Callebaut, shined instantly.</p>



<p>I could imagine sitting on a balcony overlooking beautiful views of Rome or along the Amalfi Coast on a sunny morning, sipping on a cappuccino (which is commonly seen as a ‘breakfast coffee’ in Italy) and having a bite of this cookie. After all, when in Rome (or as close to Rome as you can get), do as the Romans do.</p>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img data-attachment-id="16066" data-permalink="http://thejourneyndestination.com/2022/05/15/italian-chocolate-and-iced-sugar-star-cookies-pan-di-stelle/20220511_155752/" data-orig-file="https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_155752.jpg" data-orig-size="3349,1642" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{

}" data-image-title="20220511_155752" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_155752.jpg?w=300" data-large-file="https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_155752.jpg?w=1024" src="https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_155752.jpg?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-16066" srcset="https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_155752.jpg?w=1024 1024w, https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_155752.jpg?w=2048 2048w, https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_155752.jpg?w=150 150w, https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_155752.jpg?w=300 300w, https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_155752.jpg?w=768 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>


<p>By my third bite, my taste buds registered the Pan di Stelle more as a cookie rather than breakfast cereal, but there is a different depth in flavor in comparison to regular chocolate cookies. I feel it might be credited to the butter, as butter is a primary ingredient that is featured alongside cocoa on the package.</p>



<p>The iced sugar stars on top are lovely too. Their touch isn’t overly sweet, as cocoa is the main note. Overall, the flavor feels like home to the palates of chocolate fans.</p>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img data-attachment-id="16070" data-permalink="http://thejourneyndestination.com/2022/05/15/italian-chocolate-and-iced-sugar-star-cookies-pan-di-stelle/20220511_155956/" data-orig-file="https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_155956.jpg" data-orig-size="3212,1446" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{

}" data-image-title="20220511_155956" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_155956.jpg?w=300" data-large-file="https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_155956.jpg?w=1024" src="https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_155956.jpg?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-16070" srcset="https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_155956.jpg?w=1024 1024w, https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_155956.jpg?w=2048 2048w, https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_155956.jpg?w=150 150w, https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_155956.jpg?w=300 300w, https://thejourneyndestination.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/20220511_155956.jpg?w=768 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>


<p>The cookie is crumbly and crisp. Munching on my second cookie, I realized that this is one of those cookies that cookie dippers would enjoy with a glass of milk. While I’m not a cookie-dipper, I did enjoy the cookies in other fun ways.</p>



