<p>Although outside the metropolis, Antipolo is nevertheless classified as a city. You won’t realize you’ve left Metro Manila once you arrive here – the area and its environs are virtually urbanized. There are however, several pockets of forested hills that offer a quick escape from city life. One of these features <a href="https://shoestringdiary.wordpress.com/2018/07/16/hinulugang-taktak-rehabbing-a-waterfall/"><strong>Hinulugang Taktak</strong></a>, a waterfall that has seen better days.</p>


