<p>Shooting over, we headed to our favorite place in this part of town: Tipulo Restaurant along Sumulong Highway. Even before the pandemic, Tipulo features open-air dining. It’s actually a covered facility open on three sides. Plenty of vegetation around the place gave it a cozy feel and somewhat mitigated the scorching heat on this day.</p>


