<p>I helped myself to some chips from the snack basket. Each time I was on my way out of the lavatory back to my seat or visiting the galley for a snack, the flight attendants would ask if I needed anything to drink or needed anything in general. Love that SQ touch.</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" data-attachment-id="12761" data-permalink="http://gastronomictraveler.blog/2022/05/15/review-worlds-longest-flight-on-singapore-airlines-sq23-jfk-sin-in-business-class/pxl_20220505_101258395/" data-orig-file="https://garythegastronomictraveler.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/pxl_20220505_101258395.jpeg" data-orig-size="368,654" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{

