<p>Kaya toast and Kopi roasting atop a coal stove.</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" data-attachment-id="12773" data-permalink="http://gastronomictraveler.blog/2022/05/15/review-worlds-longest-flight-on-singapore-airlines-sq23-jfk-sin-in-business-class/pxl_20220505_231030242/" data-orig-file="https://garythegastronomictraveler.files.wordpress.com/2022/05/pxl_20220505_231030242.jpeg" data-orig-size="368,654" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{

