<p>We have got to mention a very special thing that happened. Our son who is 4 told us he wants to be a chef when he grows up and what did the hotel do? Make that happen! Dawid and Lauren the chefs, set up a little station for him with his own special chef hat and jacket and let him do some of the hard work! I can’t believe they done something like this and they will never know how much something so little has done for us as a family. I hope our son will always remember it. After our son had his special cooking session, we enjoyed a gorgeous afternoon tea with the food he made himself along with some other sandwiches, pastries and sweets.</p>



