<p>On the final day of our stay I booked in to have a Ishga back massage which I had been looking forward to for weeks as I never ever ever treat myself with treatments (I definitely will now) I had Kimberley who was so calming and gentle and had a lovely aura about her. The massage was amazing and all products used were incredible, infact I left wanting to buy them all! She sold them all so well to me and told me exactly what I would benefit from and what they would do for me.</p>



