<p>Luckily this was not the case. Instead they was just renovating it and putting in place new displays for their new offerings. Now they have greatly expanded their selection of fresh meats and offers meat of a variety of qualities and from a variety of regions. I think they now have like 3 or 4 choices of each major cut.</p>



<p>We can probably thank the fact that we’re so close to Switzerland for that. Since the Swiss have a much more responsible fiscal regime, which was especially evident during their handling of the Chinese virus scare, people in Switzerland have much more money to spend and they do come over to France a lot to do their grocery and other kinds of shopping.</p>


