<p>The Canon lens featured here is fantastic for landscape and indoor photography. I had the opportunity to photograph inside a heating plant and I decided to use this lens to capture the entirety of the building. </p>



<p>The indoor environment presented a challenge. I decided a tripod and the hdr method would most likely give me the best results. </p>



