<p>My settings on the Sony were f2.8, ISO 800 to 1600 shutter speed at around 1-80 to 1-100. The first floor of the place was well lit so I just took one regular image which you see at the start. As we moved up the levels, the place got darker. I decided on doing HDR for the darker floors and I think that worked out rather well as you will see in the photos.</p>



